examples.en: He broiled a few steaks for us. / He broiled us a few steaks.
We lay broiling in the sun.
The town was broiling in the sun.
A tavern row between scholar and townsman widens into a general broil.
examples.ru: Ссора в таверне между ученым мужем и горожанином превращается во всеобщую потасовку.
